               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist and of the angel Gäbrǝʾel (fols. 20vb, 21va, 68vb, 76ra, 81rb); names of the donors (erased and replaced); elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I (alternating with black lines), two initial lines in the incipit of sections (homilies) and of subsections (miracles); the first word in the incipit of subsections (hymns), i.e. sälam "salutation".</rubric>
